|sat_logo|

.. |sat_logo| image:: ../images/logo_sat.png

:Author: Sylvain Cormier


Purpose
-------

Scripts to run test cases via telnet to satify system tests between two machines.

Prerequisites
+++++++++++++

Both machines must be configured with ssh automatic login (ssh-keyinstall)


Files
+++++

miville.py
telnet_redux_state_machine.py
dist_telnet_sys_test7b.py

Instructions
------------

Run miville.py on each machine

::

	user@machine:~/src/miville/trunk/py/test/$python miville.py


Insert remote machine name in the concerned tests 

Run the scripts on local machine

::

	user@machine:~/src/miville/trunk/py/$trial test/telnet_redux_state_machine_test.py

